<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>Monster Hunter World Database</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bulma/0.9.3/css/bulma.min.css">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
</head>

<body>
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="title is-3 is-spaced has-text-white">Monster Hunter World <br>Armor and Weapon Database</p>
    <p class="subtitle is-spaced has-text-grey-light">This application is a resource for detailed information about weapons,
      armors, and crafting materials found in Monster Hunter World.</p>

    <div class="block">
      <h2 class="title is-5 has-text-white">Features</h2>
      <ul >
        <li><b>Search:</b> Easily find specific armors and weapons using the search feature.</li>
        <li><b>Detailed Information:</b> Get the stats, crafting requirements, and abilities of each piece of gear.</li>
        <li><b>Filter and Sort:</b> Narrow down your options by filtering.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="block">
      <h2 class="title is-5 has-text-white">Getting Started</h2>
      <p>Begin by exploring our <a href="/armors">Armor Database</a> or <a href="/weapons">Weapon Database</a>. You can
        search for specific items or use filters to find what you need for your next hunt. Each item's page provides
        detailed information about its attributes and or crafting requirements.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="block">
      <h2 class="title is-5 has-text-white">About Monster Hunter World</h2>
      <p>Monster Hunter World, developed and published by Capcom, has emerged as a pinnacle in the action
        role-playing genre, captivating gamers worldwide with its immersive gameplay, breathtaking landscapes,
        and formidable creatures. Released in 2018, this installment in the Monster Hunter series introduces a
        plethora of new features that redefine the gaming experience.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
</body>
</html>